cdata.name: CarTaxi
cdata.desc: CarTaxi is a logistics platform for evacuating and transporting cars that integrates all tow trucks in a single application, combining geolocation with blockchain technologies . Users can call for road assistance of the same standard of service worldwide, and packaging them into an Uber-like interface. The CarTaxi (CTX) is an ERC20 token based on the Ethereum blockchain. It allows project supporters to receive dividends while also featuirng a buy-back and burn system.
